h4. +Scenario+

Currently [/rest/api/2/workflow/\{id}/properties|https://docs.atlassian.com/jira/REST/server/#api/2/workflow-getProperties] is not working. According to [https://ecosystem.atlassian.net/browse/ACJIRA-688,] this endpoint doesn't exist. Instead, there exists another endpoint for retrieving Workflow Transition Properties:
{code:java}
/rest/api/2/workflow/transitions/{transitionId}/properties
{code}
h4. +Suggestion+

There should be an endpoint for Workflow Step Properties as well, which is currently not available.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
